cu.explanation_en: Setting the AMF IP address to an invalid format '999.999.999.999' will cause network interface configuration errors and AMF connection failures.

du.explanation_en: Setting the PRACH msg1 FDM to 10 will cause invalid PRACH configuration and RACH procedure failures.
du.explanation_zh: 將 PRACH msg1 FDM 設定為 10 會導致無效的 PRACH 配置，並造成 RACH 程序失敗。
